  <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
  <p>
    Daily Bible App provides a mobile application for reading Bible scriptures, accessing devotionals, following reading plans, and related spiritual content. The Service includes:
  </p>

  <h3>2.1 Core Features (Available to All Users):</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Bible text reading with multiple translations (KJV, NIV, Diodati, Almeida, and others)</li>
    <li>Daily verse feature with daily inspirational verses</li>
    <li>Basic notes and bookmarks</li>
    <li>Basic verse highlighting</li>
    <li>Reading progress tracking</li>
    <li>Devotionals and reading plans</li>
    <li>User account management and data sync</li>
    <li>Ad-supported free access (ads shown to free users)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>2.2 Pro Features (Requires Purchase):</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Ad-free experience</li>
    <li>Extended daily verse history (90 days vs 30 days for free users)</li>
    <li>Advanced notes with rich text formatting</li>
    <li>Multiple highlight colors and advanced highlighting options</li>
    <li>Advanced reading customization (font families, line spacing, themes)</li>
    <li>Enhanced saved verse organization with tags and filtering</li>
    <li>Verse collections and custom organization</li>
    <li>Additional premium features as they are added</li>
  </ul>

